      "clean_commercial": "Aïn Harrouda / Mohammedia corridor includes a major industrial area (incl. SAMIR refinery area referenced as part of the local industrial zone) . Nearby retail includes Jawhara Mall in Aïn Harrouda and Zenata Mall in the Zenata Eco-City between Casablanca and Mohammedia (Visit Casablanca – Zenata Mall ).",
      "clean_transport": "Public transport: Moovit lists bus lines 800 and 904 serving Aïn Harrouda (incl. stop “Aïn Harrouda – Centre”) (Moovit – Aïn Harrouda public transit ). Airport access: Rome2Rio estimates ~34.5 km road distance and ~32 minutes drive between Mohammed V International Airport (CMN) and Aïn Harrouda (Rome2Rio – CMN to Aïn Harrouda ). Highway access: the Aïn Harrouda junction connects to major Casablanca motorway approaches used for north-south transit (Morocco World News ).",
      "market_intel": "Aïn Harrouda commune has a population of 60,804 per Morocco's 2024 RGPH census (HCP), down slightly from 62,420 in 2014; Mohammedia Prefecture totals 514,057, up 27% from 404,648.HCP RGPH 2024. Area features mixed residential, commercial, and extensive industrial zones like Zenata; no specific density or income data found, but regional unemployment was ~18% in 2014.City Population,World Bank.",
      "competitor_analysis": "Local competitors include JR Carrosserie et Mécanique (bodywork/mechanics, Zenata industrial zone Aïn Harrouda), Lavage Auto Nabil (car wash, Aïn Harrouda), Loma Auto (garage, Route 107 km16). No verified service bays at nearby Afriquia (e.g., Hassan 2 Mohammedia ~7km), Shell, or TotalEnergies stations.Facebook JR,Telecontact Lavage Nabil.",
      "traffic_access": "Served by Route Nouaceur (RN11 towards Nouaceur Airport/Mohammedia), key corridor northeast of Casablanca. Recent ADM upgrades to Aïn Harrouda interchange (750MDH, completed 2025) handle ~140k vehicles/day, reduce congestion; ongoing widenings in Nouaceur-Casablanca.ADM,Medias24. Good accessibility via national roads.",
      "infrastructure_new": "Zenata Industrial Zone and Eco-City (90ha, residential/industrial/logistics, medical center 2025, full by 2030); new logistics hubs in Oulad Saleh/Nouaceur (550MDH, 2026); World Bank $350M rail to Zenata/Mohammedia/Nouaceur; parc logistique Zenata.Le360,World Bank.",
      "commercial_context_new": "Zenata Mall in Eco-City Aïn Harrouda (one of North Africa's largest); Marjane Mohammedia (~10km); local pharmacies/markets; developing offices/schools in Zenata. No major souks/hospitals specified nearby.Visit Casablanca.",
      "fleet_potential": "Visite Technique NEAB controle technique center in central Aïn Harrouda; taxi ranks/services to Mohammedia; car rentals in Mohammedia (1ServiceCar, Jacaranda); delivery/logistics firms active (Ameex, HyperColis, RaitheXpress) amid industrial growth.Facebook NEAB,Yandex Taxi.",
      "key_insight": "High-traffic industrial/residential corridor with growing logistics/eco-city developments and infrastructure upgrades supports strong quick-service bay demand; limited specialized competitors within 2km present opportunity."
